e-llm-wiki-md). [](https://gist.github.com/karpathy/442a6bf555914893e9891c11519de94f#llm-wiki). Instead of just retrieving from raw documents at query time, the LLM **incrementally builds and maintains a persistent wiki** — a structured, interlinked collection of markdown files that sits between you and the raw sources. **The schema** — a document (e.g. CLAUDE.md for Claude Code or AGENTS.md for Codex) that tells the LLM how the wiki is structured, what the conventions are, and what workflows to follow when ingesting sources, answering questions, or maintaining the wiki. The wiki side is meant to feel like a lightweight Confluence that lives with the code: raw sources stay separate, the agent maintains structured markdown pages, `index.md` and `log.md` make it discoverable, and schema rules keep future agents from treating it as just another notes folder. > [![Image 34: autosci_fig1_v1-第 15 页 drawio png](https://private-user-images.githubusercontent.com/167013924/601264634-039ae53b-b3b8-440a-b98e-e715fe2c8f51.svg?jwt=eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJpc3MiOiJnaXRodWIuY29tIiwiYXVkIjoicmF3LmdpdGh1YnVzZXJjb250ZW50LmNvbSIsImtleSI6ImtleTUiLCJleHAiOjE3ODE2MTg3MzksIm5iZiI6MTc4MTYxODQzOSwicGF0aCI6Ii8xNjcwMTM5MjQvNjAxMjY0NjM0LTAzOWFlNTNiLWIzYjgtNDQwYS1iOThlLWU3MTVmZTJjOGY1MS5zdmc_.jRG6-hRQDkAnpCir4MOWEp4hUJ5Hy5TjCa3MiV2kMjc)](https://private-user-images.githubusercontent.com/167013924/601264634-039ae53b-b3b8-440a-b98e-e715fe2c8f51.svg?jwt=eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJpc3MiOiJnaXRodWIuY29tIiwiYXVkIjoicmF3LmdpdGh1YnVzZXJjb250ZW50LmNvbSIsImtleSI6ImtleTUiLCJleHAiOjE3ODE2MTg3MzksIm5iZiI6MTc4MTYxODQzOSwicGF0aCI6Ii8xNjcwMTM5MjQvNjAxMjY0NjM0LTAzOWFlNTNiLWIzYjgtNDQwYS1iOThlLWU3MTVmZTJjOGY1MS5zdmc_.jRG6-hRQDkAnpCir4MOWEp4hUJ5Hy5TjCa3MiV2kMjc)Karpathy's pattern (immutable raw/ → an LLM-compiled wiki/ → a CLAUDE.md schema) is the exact foundation of AutoSci — an agent that turns the wiki into a research memory and then does autonomous science on top of it.", "score": 0.